snippet.title: THE BEST NEW .IO GAME?? TANKWARS.IO - BECOMING THE BIGGEST!! (Games like Agar.io / Slither.io)
snippet.description:
Join us in a BRAND NEW .IO GAME called TANKWARS.IO (similar to agar.io / slither.io)!! Will this one be the best IO GAME EVER? I don't know, but I surely know that the graphics are pretty awesome and the gameplay is pretty cool once you get the hang of it!

I'm also going to try and go back to daily uploads, so HURRAY for that, I guess :D Sorry I haven't done much lately, just had a bunch of computer-related issues which made me feel bad, so I just didn't feel like recording videos and got totally out of it sadly lol, but I AM BACK BABYYYYYYYYYY :)
